		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Referring to the NES joyport. Just wondering if someone can tell me if this is correct:
<br />
<br />1. brown (ground)
<br />2. red (clock)
<br />3. orange (latch)
<br />4. yellow (serial input from gamepad)
<br />
<br />5. white (no connection)
<br />6. blue (n.c.)
<br />
<br />7. purple (+5V)
<br />
<br />(The numbers listed above are the actual numbers imprinted on the gamepad jack/port.)
<br />
<br />Is this correct?
<br />
<br />Thank again,
<br />T

		

